[h1]Mod Introduction[/h1]
[b]All Versions[/b]
This mod adds a "Move to" button to the info bar of some immovable objects in the game. Press this button, select a location, and the selected object will instantly move to the position chosen by the tool.

Please Note:
1.If a moved object acts weirdly, just reload your save.
2.Known Issue: Moving objects while paused right after loading frequently causes crashes that are hard to reproduce.
3.To move the Hermit’s Shack (Solemn Tech Shipping Container), you must move its paired mailbox.

